px;\">Many thanks</span>,</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 160%;\"><span style=\"font-family: Bitter; line-height: 22.4px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 22.4px; font-size: 14px;\">Leo Hyperion,</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 160%;\"><span style=\"font-family: Bitter; line-height: 22.4px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 22.4px; font-size: 14px;\">HEAD OF PARTNERSHIPS</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 160%;\"> </p>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n  <!--[if (!mso)&(!IE)]><!--></div><!--<![endif]-->\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--[if (mso)|(IE)]></td><![endif]-->\r\n      <!--[if (mso)|(IE)]></tr></table></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n    <!--[if (mso)|(IE)]></td></tr></table><![endif]-->\r\n    </td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <!--[if mso]></div><![endif]-->\r\n  <!--[if IE]></div><![endif]-->\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n";
   
